short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Finds the Athena Department ID and returns the current Tablespace and Department ID for the logged in user

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension watches for an Athena Health screen and reports the DEPARTMENTID back to the background script, which in turns reports it back to a Native Messaging app.
